Development Committee did support the program 
for the goals of Corpus Christi. A number of

08:07.389 --> 08:15.280
committees were established, and the goals were 
outlined and published. But unfortunately,

08:17.102 --> 08:27.516
not very much has been done to follow up on it. It's a 
nice book, and quite a few people have it, but very

08:30.010 --> 08:39.704
little reference is ever made to it now. Not nearly 
